OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bill
OL,4,CJohnston
OL,6,F, plenty of water splashes and what-
OL,7,Fnot. It was only when we hit the beach
OL,8,Fand the ramp went down that I remember
OL,9,Fseeing the signs and the barbed wire
OL,10,Fand the wreckage - "This is Enemy
OL,11,FTerritory."
OL,13,F"That's when it really dawned on me.
OL,15,F"I got ashore dry, just drove off the
OL,16,Fcraft onto the beach to wherever we
OL,17,Fwere going. At that point I wasn't
OL,18,Fscared. Naive perhaps is a good word."
