OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bill
OL,4,CJohnston
OL,6,FMr Johnston would sometimes drive
OL,7,Fahead of the guns to spot targets and
OL,8,Fother times act as a wireless operator
OL,9,Fin the tanks.
OL,11,F"Sometimes it was a jeep," he said.
OL,13,F"Other times it was an 800 weight
OL,14,Fwireless truck. Whatever, that was my
OL,15,Frank. I wasn't a gunner, I wasn't a
OL,16,Fprivate, I was a driver and wireless
OL,17,Foperator.'"
