OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bill
OL,4,CJohnston
OL,6,F"So far as I know I was knocked out
OL,7,Ffor two or three days and I have
OL,8,Fflashing memories of civilians, Nuns.
OL,9,FI was flown home and fetched up at the
OL,10,FRoyal Infirmary in Cardiff. That was
OL,11,Fthe end of my war."
